This is the root directory of PSCF C++/Cuda package. See the README.md
file for basic instructions on usage.

Subdirectories:
  bin/       default installation directory for executables
  bld/       build directory for out-of-source builds 
  data/      read-only data files (i.e., space group description files)
  doc/       documentation files
  make/      makefiles and makefile fragments installed by setup script
  src/       C++ and CUDA source code
  scripts/   scripts written in python, matlab or other languages

Files: 
  CONTENTS  - this file
  README    - brief intro to package
  setup     - executable script to setup build system prior to compilation
  makefile  - main makefile for global clean up (not used for compilation)

